org.apache.drill.exec.store.table.function

Class TableParamDef

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.exec.store.table.function.TableParamDef

  • public final class TableParamDef
extends Object
    Definition of table parameters, contains parameter name, class type, type status (optional / required). May also contain action this parameter can perform for the given value and table.
